      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large molcajete over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the sliced galangal and cook for an additional 2 minutes",
    "Add the chopped carrot and celery and cook until they begin to soften",
    "Add the sliced mushrooms and cook until they release their liquid and start to brown",
    "Add the vegetable broth, tomato paste, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired"
  ],
